DAN JURGENS: Yeah, comic.

00:30:02.415 --> 00:30:03.270
Streaky's the cat.

00:30:03.270 --> 00:30:03.660
BRIAN MICHAEL BENDIS:
Streaky's the cat.

00:30:03.660 --> 00:30:04.880
I apologize.

00:30:04.880 --> 00:30:05.710
Again, I'm new.

00:30:05.710 --> 00:30:06.630
DAN JURGENS: Yeah.

