They're Googling it right now.

00:30:12.280 --> 00:30:13.480
Yeah, that's all real stuff.

00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:14.000
DAN JURGENS: Yeah.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:16.150
BRIAN MICHAEL BENDIS: Everything
